13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

13/ The worst question of all is “Do you like it?”. Never ask.

#ownersummit
@MichaelAleo Come on Mike…i’m a professional tweeter :)

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

12.5/ Most clients have no idea what kind of feedback you’re looking for.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

12/ Not guiding the feedback loop. “What do you think?” is the worst question.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

11/ Reacting to questions as change requests. “Why is this blue” > “I can change it" 

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

10/ Talking about how hard you worked or how busy you are. It should look effortless.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

9.5/ If you ask for opinions on design, don’t come crying when they give them to you.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

9/ Mentioning typefaces. Clients don’t give a shit. /cc @zbgoodwin

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

8.5/ You do not need to defend your design decisions in real-time. Mule it over.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

8/ Getting defensive. Your work is not you. You are not your work.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

7.75/ Work towards a crescendo. Never be afraid to let the spirit move you.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

7.5/ You are promoting! You are promoting the idea the work will succeed. 

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

7/ Reading a script. THIS IS A LIVE SHOW!

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

7/ Reading a script. THIS IS LIVE SHOW!

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

6/ Taking notes. Your energy should be focused on selling the work. It’s submissive.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

5.5/ Not selling the benefits of the work - what it will do for the business.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

5/ Giving the real estate tour - talking about where u positioned things on the site

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

4/ Not setting the stage properly. Let clients know why they’re here/where we are.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

3/ Starting with an apology. Every time you apologize you’re freaking the client out.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

2/ Not getting off your ass. A client should never not know you’re leading the room.

#ownersummit

13 Mistakes Designers Make by @monteiro

1/ You are not there to be the client’s friend.

#ownersummit
